               <code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>How Supplied/Storage and Handling</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>2.0% Neutral Sodium Fluoride (0.9% Fluoride Ion) oral solution supplied in a plastic bottle with child-resistant closure containing 64 fl. oz. (1.89 L). Store at room temperature. Protect from freezing. Do not store in direct sunlight.</paragraph>
